# Public build-time config for hosted deploys (Vercel). All values here are
# safe to expose: the anon key is a publishable key, the URL/domain are public.
# The LLM key is NOT here — chat uses the edge-function gateway (set
# GEMINI_API_KEY as a Supabase secret to enable real answers on the host).
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://khjzoboeshgtymijzcaf.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_soHegVbA7TCZ-ivucBg9ag_syAr78Oh
VITE_STUDENT_EMAIL_DOMAIN=students.merzal.local
# LLM key intentionally NOT set here — the hosted site routes chat through the
# Supabase `chat` edge function, which holds the key server-side (see edge
# function v2). The bundle never carries the key. To use a different model on
# Vercel, change CAMPUS_MODEL / WORLD_MODEL via Supabase secrets or update the
# edge function FALLBACK constants.
